County cities: Santa Paula: 28 Simi Valley: 28 Oxnard: 14 Port Hueneme: 14 
Thousand Oaks: 13 Fillmore: 12 Ojai: 9 Ventura: 9 Camarillo: 4 Moorpark: 2 
Source: County Cultural Heritage Board  
