<DATE>
<P>
October 24, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 2; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
336 words 
</P>
