<HEADLINE>
<P>
AT LEAST 2 KILLED IN GANG SHOOTOUT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 At least two people were reported killed and seven others critically or 
seriously wounded in what police characterized as a gang-related shooting in 
South-Central Los Angeles late Sunday night. 
</P>
<P>
 Newton Division officers said the shootout at 53rd Street and Towne Avenue 
involved handguns and at least one shotgun. 
</P>
<P>
 Police had no further details available. 
</P>
