 * What Happened Sunday: Democrat Kathleen Brown addressed the state council of 
the California Teachers Assn. in Burlingame, lashing out at Republican Pete 
Wilson as a "career politician" and for his support of Proposition 187, the 
ballot measure that would bar illegal immigrants from receiving state-financed 
