<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102494-0213 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 091829 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 24, 1994, Monday, Valley Edition 
</P>
