<TEXT>
<P>
 Voices -- An article in Thursday's Calendar about the new Disney animated film 
"Pocahontas" referred incompletely to the voices supplied to the title 
character. Irene Bedard supplies the speaking voice of Pocahontas, and Judy 
Kuhn supplies the singing voice. 
</P>
